data.description: Discover the charm of this impeccable 3-bed, 2-bath gem! We're thrilled to present a home that combines modern comfort with classic elegance, offering the perfect canvas for your next chapter. It has a bright and airy open floor plan with tile and wood floorings. Step into the backyard retreat—a haven for relaxation and gatherings. This home also boasts the convenience of a garage and offering secure parking. Don't miss the opportunity to make this stunning home yours.
